    <h3>For Users</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>
            <h4>How do I search for a property?</h4>
            <p>Use the search bar on the homepage to filter properties by location, price range, and type (holiday rentals, long-term rentals, or homes for sale).</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <h4>How do I book a holiday rental?</h4>
            <p>Select the property you are interested in, choose your dates, and click on the "Book Now" button. You will be guided through the payment process.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <h4>What if I need to cancel my booking?</h4>
            <p>You can cancel your booking from your account dashboard under the "My Bookings" section. Please review our cancellation policy for any applicable fees.</p>
        </li>
    </ul>

    <h3>For Property Owners</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>
            <h4>How do I list my property?</h4>
            <p>Go to the "List Your Property" section, fill in the details, upload photos, and submit. Once approved, your property will be live on our site.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <h4>How do I manage my listings?</h4>
            <p>You can manage your listings from your account dashboard. Here you can edit details, update pricing, and view booking requests.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <h4>What are the fees for listing my property?</h4>
            <p>We charge a small commission on each booking made through our platform. Details of the fees can be found in the "Fees & Pricing" section of your dashboard.</p>
        </li>
